  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >H+H=H2 is a sokoban-like game that contains pseudo chemistry </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220520/extras/9e0c47e1fc734042ca2fe550f156c976.avif?t=1748579489\" width=300 height=80 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Cute Pixel Style </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Chemistry based fake chemistry mechanics </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 60 Hand-craft Levels </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Solitaire </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220520/extras/340ca2cfcfab067ad2b7c7e50b81566f.avif?t=1748579489\" width=300 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Basic mechanics requires you to collision each Hydrogen atoms makes no Hydrogen atoms exists in the level </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >H + H = H2 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >H + H2 = H3 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >H3 couldn't be pushed </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220520/extras/90e62ab14b1e827bc71b2f482c3d0c73.poster.avif?t=1748579489\" width=304 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220520/extras/90e62ab14b1e827bc71b2f482c3d0c73.webm?t=1748579489\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220520/extras/90e62ab14b1e827bc71b2f482c3d0c73.mp4?t=1748579489\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you process this game, there will be more mechanics: Like He atom could push everything including H3(?) atom etc. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220520/extras/0673d8d23fdcfdde4fc855044e058c64.avif?t=1748579489\" width=300 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A unique solitaire inspired by Zachtronics's Fortune’s Foundation</p>",
